F4A-24 — List Decommissioned Apps
Inside Prior Gates Incomplete → If No, after Loop Removed CPs (sibling level, not nested). Dataverse → List rows.
Table: Staged Records
Filter rows: fx → concat('_pei_importcycle_value eq ', variables('varImportCycleID'), ' and pei_entitytype eq 890920001 and pei_whatchanged eq 890920003')
Rename to: List Decommissioned Apps
Note: Entity Type = Application (890920001), What Changed = Decommissioned (890920003).

F4A-25 — Loop Decommissioned Apps
Apply to each, after List Decommissioned Apps.
Select output: fx → outputs('List_Decommissioned_Apps')?['body/value']
Rename to: Loop Decommissioned Apps

F4A-26 — Find Decommissioned App Record
Inside Loop Decommissioned Apps. Dataverse → List rows.
Table: Applications
Filter rows: fx → concat('pei_displayname eq ''', items('Loop_Decommissioned_Apps')?['pei_name'], '''')
Rename to: Find Decommissioned App Record

F4A-27 — Condition: Decommissioned App Found
Inside Loop Decommissioned Apps, after Find Decommissioned App Record.
Left: fx → length(outputs('Find_Decommissioned_App_Record')?['body/value'])
Operator: is greater than
Right: 0
Rename to: Decommissioned App Found

F4A-28 — List Applicability For Decommissioned App
Inside Decommissioned App Found → If Yes. Dataverse → List rows.
Table: Applicability
Filter rows: fx → concat('_pei_application_value eq ', first(outputs('Find_Decommissioned_App_Record')?['body/value'])?['pei_applicationid'], ' and pei_applicabilitystatus eq 890920000')
Rename to: List Applicability For Decommissioned App
Note: Filter uses _pei_application_value (Applicability's App lookup field in OData). Same pattern as F4A-18 but by App instead of CP. Scopes across all cycles, Active records only.
